00:04:22,981 --> 00:04:24,262
through the matches,

98
00:04:24,262 --> 00:04:26,104
the story of progression that you're telling yourself.

99
00:04:26,104 --> 00:04:29,206
This also applies to systemic games like Rimworld,

100
00:04:29,206 --> 00:04:32,088
