00:37:55,298 --> 00:37:58,339
This was the first version of the dinosaur.

889
00:37:58,339 --> 00:38:02,501
This is how we tested it.

890
00:38:02,501 --> 00:38:05,122
This is how we saw if like, hey, can this even work?

